# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# PRODUCTION DEPLOYMENT REQUIREMENTS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# The following variables are REQUIRED for production deployment and will be
# validated before build/deployment. Run `pnpm validate:env:prod` to check.
